<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,151,933]" pageId="27" pageNumber="522">
<typeStatus box="[199,297,152,176]" pageId="27" pageNumber="522">Paratype</typeStatus>
female: larger than male, otherwise identical, except dorsum slightly more elevated and tectiform, broadly arched in lateral view.
